INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c0] ON [c].[CategoryId] = [c0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c1].[Id], [c1].[CartoonId], [c1].[CountryId], [c1].[CreatedAt], [c2].[Id] AS [Id0], [c2].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [c2].[Image], [c2].[Name]
    FROM [CountryCartoons] AS [c1]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c2] ON [c1].[CountryId] = [c2].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [c].[Id] = [t].[CartoonId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c3].[Id], [c3].[CartoonId], [c3].[CreatedAt], [c3].[StudioId], [s].[Id] AS [Id0], [s].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [s].[Image], [s].[Name]
    FROM [CartoonStudios] AS [c3]
    INNER JOIN [Studios] AS [s] ON [c3].[StudioId] = [s].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[CartoonId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c4].[Id], [c4].[CartoonId], [c4].[CollectionId], [c4].[CreatedAt], [c5].[Id] AS [Id0], [c5].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [c5].[Image], [c5].[Name]
    FROM [CartoonCollections] AS [c4]
    INNER JOIN [Collections] AS [c5] ON [c4].[CollectionId] = [c5].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[CartoonId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c6].[Id], [c6].[CartoonId], [c6].[CreatedAt], [c6].[GenreId], [g].[Id] AS [Id0], [g].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [g].[Name]
    FROM [CartoonGenres] AS [c6]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [c6].[GenreId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [c].[Id] = [t2].[CartoonId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c7].[Id], [c7].[CartoonId], [c7].[CreatedAt], [c7].[PersonId], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [p].[FullName]
    FROM [CartoonDirectors] AS [c7]
    INNER JOIN [Persons] AS [p] ON [c7].[PersonId] = [p].[Id]
) AS [t3] ON [c].[Id] = [t3].[CartoonId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c8].[Id], [c8].[CartoonId], [c8].[CreatedAt], [c8].[PersonId], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [p0].[FullName]
    FROM [CartoonActors] AS [c8]
    INNER JOIN [Persons] AS [p0] ON [c8].[PersonId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [c].[Id] = [t4].[CartoonId]
WHERE [c].[Id] IN (38, 39, 40, 43, 49, 50, 56, 57, 64, 66)
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [c0].[Id], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t3].[Id], [t3].[Id0], [t4].[Id]

    FROM [CartoonDirectors] AS [c1]
    INNER JOIN [Persons] AS [p] ON [c1].[PersonId] = [p].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CartoonId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c2].[Id], [c2].[CartoonId], [c2].[CreatedAt], [c2].[PersonId], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [p0].[FullName]
    FROM [CartoonActors] AS [c2]
    INNER JOIN [Persons] AS [p0] ON [c2].[PersonId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[CartoonId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c3].[Id], [c3].[CartoonId], [c3].[CreatedAt], [c3].[GenreId], [g].[Id] AS [Id0], [g].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [g].[Name]
    FROM [CartoonGenres] AS [c3]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [c3].[GenreId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[CartoonId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c4].[Id], [c4].[CartoonId], [c4].[CreatedAt], [c4].[StudioId], [s].[Id] AS [Id0], [s].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [s].[Image], [s].[Name]
    FROM [CartoonStudios] AS [c4]
    INNER JOIN [Studios] AS [s] ON [c4].[StudioId] = [s].[Id]
) AS [t3] ON [t].[Id] = [t3].[CartoonId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c5].[Id], [c5].[CartoonId], [c5].[CollectionId], [c5].[CreatedAt], [c6].[Id] AS [Id0], [c6].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [c6].[Image], [c6].[Name]
    FROM [CartoonCollections] AS [c5]
    INNER JOIN [Collections] AS [c6] ON [c5].[CollectionId] = [c6].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [t].[Id] = [t4].[CartoonId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c7].[Id], [c7].[CartoonId], [c7].[CountryId], [c7].[CreatedAt], [c8].[Id] AS [Id0], [c8].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [c8].[Image], [c8].[Name]
    FROM [CountryCartoons] AS [c7]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c8] ON [c7].[CountryId] = [c8].[Id]
) AS [t5] ON [t].[Id] = [t5].[CartoonId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t3].[Id], [t3].[Id0], [t4].[Id], [t4].[Id0], [t5].[Id]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[CartoonId]

(@p57, @p58, @p59, 1)) AS i ([CartoonId], [CountryId], [CreatedAt], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([CartoonId], [CountryId], [CreatedAt])
VALUES (i.[CartoonId], i.[CountryId], i.[CreatedAt])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted8;

SELECT [i].[Id] FROM @inserted8 i
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[CreatedAt], [t].[Image], [t].[Name], [t].[PlayerUrl], [t].[Plot], [t].[Year], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreatedAt], [c0].[Name], [r].[Id], [r].[CartoonId], [r].[CreatedAt], [r].[UserId], [r].[Value]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [c].[Id], [c].[CategoryId], [c].[CreatedAt], [c].[Image], [c].[Name], [c].[PlayerUrl], [c].[Plot], [c].[Year]
    FROM [Cartoons] AS [c]
    ORDER BY [c].[CreatedAt] DESC
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c0] ON [t].[CategoryId] = [c0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Ratings] AS [r] ON [t].[Id] = [r].[CartoonId]
ORDER BY [t].[CreatedAt] DESC, [t].[Id], [c0].[Id]

FROM [CartoonSliders] AS [c]
INNER JOIN [Cartoons] AS [c0] ON [c].[CartoonId] = [c0].[Id]

) AS [t] ON [c0].[Id] = [t].[CartoonId]

FROM [Cartoons] AS [c]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c0] ON [c].[CategoryId] = [c0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c1].[Id], [c1].[CartoonId], [c1].[CountryId], [c1].[CreatedAt], [c2].[Id] AS [Id0], [c2].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [c2].[Image], [c2].[Name]
    FROM [CountryCartoons] AS [c1]
    INNER JOIN [Countries] AS [c2] ON [c1].[CountryId] = [c2].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [c].[Id] = [t].[CartoonId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c3].[Id], [c3].[CartoonId], [c3].[CreatedAt], [c3].[StudioId], [s].[Id] AS [Id0], [s].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [s].[Image], [s].[Name]
    FROM [CartoonStudios] AS [c3]
    INNER JOIN [Studios] AS [s] ON [c3].[StudioId] = [s].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [c].[Id] = [t0].[CartoonId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c4].[Id], [c4].[CartoonId], [c4].[CollectionId], [c4].[CreatedAt], [c5].[Id] AS [Id0], [c5].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [c5].[Image], [c5].[Name]
    FROM [CartoonCollections] AS [c4]
    INNER JOIN [Collections] AS [c5] ON [c4].[CollectionId] = [c5].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [c].[Id] = [t1].[CartoonId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c6].[Id], [c6].[CartoonId], [c6].[CreatedAt], [c6].[GenreId], [g].[Id] AS [Id0], [g].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [g].[Name]
    FROM [CartoonGenres] AS [c6]
    INNER JOIN [Genres] AS [g] ON [c6].[GenreId] = [g].[Id]
) AS [t2] ON [c].[Id] = [t2].[CartoonId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c7].[Id], [c7].[CartoonId], [c7].[CreatedAt], [c7].[PersonId], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [p].[FullName]
    FROM [CartoonDirectors] AS [c7]
    INNER JOIN [Persons] AS [p] ON [c7].[PersonId] = [p].[Id]
) AS [t3] ON [c].[Id] = [t3].[CartoonId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c8].[Id], [c8].[CartoonId], [c8].[CreatedAt], [c8].[PersonId], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [p0].[FullName]
    FROM [CartoonActors] AS [c8]
    INNER JOIN [Persons] AS [p0] ON [c8].[PersonId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [c].[Id] = [t4].[CartoonId]
WHERE [c].[Id] IN (38, 39, 40, 43, 49, 50, 56, 57, 64, 66)
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [c0].[Id], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t3].[Id], [t3].[Id0], [t4].[Id]

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c7].[Id], [c7].[CartoonId], [c7].[CreatedAt], [c7].[PersonId], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [p].[FullName]
    FROM [CartoonDirectors] AS [c7]
    INNER JOIN [Persons] AS [p] ON [c7].[PersonId] = [p].[Id]
) AS [t3] ON [c].[Id] = [t3].[CartoonId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c8].[Id], [c8].[CartoonId], [c8].[CreatedAt], [c8].[PersonId], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [p0].[FullName]
    FROM [CartoonActors] AS [c8]
    INNER JOIN [Persons] AS [p0] ON [c8].[PersonId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [t4] ON [c].[Id] = [t4].[CartoonId]
WHERE [c].[Id] IN (38, 39, 40, 43, 49, 50, 56, 57, 64, 66)
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [c0].[Id], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0], [t2].[Id], [t2].[Id0], [t3].[Id], [t3].[Id0], [t4].[Id]

FROM [Studios] AS [s]
LEFT JOIN [CartoonStudios] AS [c0] ON [s].[Id] = [c0].[StudioId]
WHERE EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM [CartoonStudios] AS [c]
    WHERE [s].[Id] = [c].[StudioId])
ORDER BY [s].[Id]
